<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/ayat/1/point/b> legal:hasText "pelindungan kesehatan dari risiko kerusakan organ; dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/ayat/1> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/ayat/1/point/c> legal:hasKey "c" .
